Description:
    Creates a login page and reset password page where users can login with
    their Infopark CRM user credentials. This generator is part of the
    `cms:kickstart` generator.

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:login_page`

    CMS: obj_class LoginPage
    CMS: attribute headline (string)
    CMS: attribute content (html)
    CMS: attribute sort_key (string)
    CMS: attribute show_in_navigation (enum)

    CMS: obj_class ResetPasswordPage
    CMS: attribute headline (string)
    CMS: attribute content (html)
    CMS: attribute sort_key (string)
    CMS: attribute show_in_navigation (enum)